to the water in the middle
of a category three hurricane-

267
00:16:02,166 --> 00:16:03,949
Yeah, just stop it, Jesse.
All right?

268
00:16:03,950 --> 00:16:05,465
Stop it.

269
00:16:09,828 --> 00:16:11,623
See you around, brett.

270
00:16:16,601 --> 00:16:17,875
Sorry.

