00:20:25,801 --> 00:20:26,851
Yes, you do. Come on, get up.

348
00:20:26,852 --> 00:20:28,481
You're gonna take us to him.

349
00:20:33,648 --> 00:20:35,393
"For as long
as we're the minority,

