364
00:21:05,401 --> 00:21:08,492
How about that?
A fallen priest.

365
00:21:09,201 --> 00:21:12,637
- Why did you do it?
- Because he misled me.

366
00:21:12,638 --> 00:21:14,480
I really believed
that god saved my life

367
