368
00:21:17,469 --> 00:21:19,356
But now I know differently.

369
00:21:19,399 --> 00:21:21,175
And Tom knew all along.

370
00:21:21,780 --> 00:21:23,478
So what do you think
saved you?

371
00:21:24,844 --> 00:21:26,448
Evil.

372
00:21:30,329 --> 00:21:32,840
I don't think he's gonna
like your theory much better.

373
00:21:34,922 --> 00:21:36,213
You wanted your man,
I got him for you.

374
00:21:36,214 --> 00:21:38,077
But I'm confused about
a couple things-

375
00:21:38,078 --> 00:21:40,095
When did he get back
from Iraq?

376
00:21:41,071 --> 00:21:43,520
A few months ago. Why?

377
00:21:43,623 --> 00:21:45,165
Well, you've got
such a small hospital here,

378
