to discuss, sheriff?

380
00:21:50,728 --> 00:21:51,710
Major.

381
00:21:52,668 --> 00:21:53,500
Excuse me?

382
00:21:53,501 --> 00:21:54,549
Well, if you're gonna
make this formal,

