Three crewmen died.

392
00:22:18,489 --> 00:22:19,459
Yeah,
and a fourth managed

393
00:22:19,460 --> 00:22:21,588
to find his way to a ranger
station in the glades,

394
00:22:21,589 --> 00:22:23,429
