00:24:22,818 --> 00:24:24,363
"Which side"?

431
00:24:24,507 --> 00:24:25,468
Yeah.

432
00:24:26,606 --> 00:24:27,785
I'm just worried that Jesse's

433
00:24:27,786 --> 00:24:29,043
in such a bad place right now,

434
00:24:29,044 --> 00:24:32,722
that whatever side he chooses
is gonna be the wrong one.

